    "We present the basic statistics of AdvancedIF in Table 1.",
    "We also compare AdvancedIF with existing verifiable and rubric-based instruction following benchmarks in Table 2 and show that AdvancedIF is the only one whose prompts and rubrics are manually created by human experts and has dialogs with multi-turn conversation and system prompts.",
    "This comprehensive coverage enables AdvancedIF to best simulate real user-bot interactions and set up high standards for LLMs' IF capabilities.",
    "Prompts Collection.",
